{"tid":1134828,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"成都親子樂園滑梯意外！　14遊客「衝出防護」釀2死12傷","createTime":"2019-05-02T02:37:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-02T06:48:24.000Z","uid":39464,"like":31,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"97133fd59039b312ac48d6412e696bed3810f975","tid":1134828,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T02:37:12.000Z","msg":"四川成都親子樂園「孩子的院子」1日發生旅客衝出溜滑梯防護設施的事故，截至2日凌晨2點，已有2名成人送醫後不治、12名傷患正在醫院進行搶救。對此，成都天府新區太平街道辦事處發布通告稱，目前已控制遊樂園相關負責人，也責令遊樂園停止營運。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4065/d4065487.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4065%2Fd4065487.jpg&h=d34fbc86&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n通報稱，事故發生後，相關部門與街道辦事處立刻動員前往，在進行搶救傷患的同時，全力安撫傷患家屬與善後工作，並按照程序啟動事故調查、控制遊樂園相關負責人。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，警方、消防隊與各救難單位立刻到達現場救援傷者。孩子的院子內部有許多此類「無重力設施」；而發生事故的是遊樂園裡「最長的」溜滑梯，總滑行時間超過3分鐘。<br />\n據了解，發生事故的遊客是在遊玩「高速溜滑梯」設施時，因為滑行速度太快，出現遊客「塞車」的情形，導致「後方追撞前方」、從遊樂設施的「橡皮輪胎上」滑落。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4065/d4065464.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4065%2Fd4065464.jpg&h=950260f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n據了解，孩子的院子位在成都太平鎮里，是由藝術家用5年的時間打造的「院子」，提供親子家庭戶外的森林遊樂園，內部區域分成鏡園、木園、網園與沙灘園等共八大項目，其中又以長235公尺的「世界上最長溜滑梯」聞名。<br />\n據悉，孩子的院子2017年7月8日正式營運，但是開幕的第二天，也就是7月9日，便發生「綠色鋼管連接褐色麻繩」的童橋「壓住一男一女」的事故，當時遊樂園官方僅解釋「遊客爆滿，管理失控，造成3人摔傷事故。」孩子的遊樂園官方微博9日晚間7點50分發布「從7月10日起暫停營業」的公告，詳細原因並未提及。<br />\n網友在談論這次的溜滑梯意外時談到，有小朋友摔了、有的「腿摔斷了」、有的「手摔斷了」，甚至還有3歲小孩的「腿摔斷了」、還沒找到父母；也有網友感嘆，「又出事了」、「我就在現場，太嚇人了」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4065/d4065486.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4065%2Fd4065486.jpg&h=1fe5bc18&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20190502/1435125.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20190502%2F1435125.htm&d=P2v3VPQ3iBAPr6cjv61qmXdC2y4sA4GELDQI6FTBpyI%3D&h=215d00e0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20190502/1435125.htm</a>"},{"pid":"1b346234a0e118d76a9fbc726e22e7e4e1dfe060","tid":1134828,"uid":19126,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T02:40:10.000Z","msg":"跌死得一兩個人算咩新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfff07e1e17d9b6f9a44f7053a59683f77bc1ded","tid":1134828,"uid":40470,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T02:40:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n見到隻蝗個痛苦樣笑左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6363b7cf10c02f3cf65832a69546cb78fc5a766b","tid":1134828,"uid":39464,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T02:41:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20190502/photo/bkn-20190502055040057-0502_00952_001_01p.jpg?20190502091905\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20190502%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190502055040057-0502_00952_001_01p.jpg%3F20190502091905&h=73ec73b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20190502/photo/bkn-20190502055040057-0502_00952_001_02p.jpg?20190502091905\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20190502%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190502055040057-0502_00952_001_02p.jpg%3F20190502091905&h=2bf2da9e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20190502/photo/bkn-20190502055040057-0502_00952_001_04p.jpg?20190502091905\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20190502%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190502055040057-0502_00952_001_04p.jpg%3F20190502091905&h=9bcf88ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20190502/bkn-20190502055040057-0502_00952_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fh